Main objectives:
- Create a fully functional Connect 4 game.
- It should include a starting menu.
- It should include an basic AI which will play with the user.
- The user should have the ability to start a new game after completing the previous one.
- The menu should also include a "Help" option, which lists some basic instructions and rules of the game.

Additional features which we would like to add:
- Upgrade the basic AI. We could program it to make smarter moves and also give comments when the user makes a mistake.
